        {{#language_ja}}
          <li>NoEjectDelayはEjectキーの遅延を無効化します。</li>
          <li>NoEjectDelayはF12Eject機能を無効化します。</li>
        {{/language_ja}}
      </ul>

      <div class="alert alert-warning">
        NEWS:
        <small>
          {{#format_date}}
            2014-02-27
          {{/format_date}}
        </small>
        <br />
        <br />
        {{#language_en}}
          Please upgrade to NoEjectDelay-5.4.0.
          <a href="#show-version">(How to know the installed version.)</a><br />
